25|$|The {{curvature}} of the universe can be measured through multipole moments in the spectrum of the <b>cosmic</b> <b>background</b> <b>radiation.</b> As to date, analysis of the radiation patterns recorded by the WMAP spacecraft hints that the universe has a flat topology. This {{would be consistent with}} an infinite physical universe.|$|E
